
Compile:
  % (optional) sh -x autogen.sh
  % ./configure
  % make
  % make install

Setup:
  1. add syslog.conf a line about local7 facility.
     local7.*                       /var/log/local7.log

  2. touch /var/log/local7.log
     % sudo touch /var/log/local7.log

  3. (optional) add configuration in newsyslog.conf.
     % sudo cp $(srcdir)/misc/horus-newsyslog.conf /etc/newsyslog.d/

Usage:

  Using key calculation tools:

      % ~/bin/horus_key <offset> <masterkey>
      % ~/bin/horus_key2 <offset> <masterkey>
      % python misc/python.py <offset> <masterkey>

  Using library:

    csh, tcsh:

      To start using libhorus:
      % source $(prefix)/etc/libhorus-start.csh

      To stop using libhorus:
      % source $(prefix)/etc/libhorus-stop.csh

    sh, bash, zsh:

      To start using libhorus:
      % . $(prefix)/etc/libhorus-start.sh

      To stop using libhorus:
      % . $(prefix)/etc/libhorus-stop.sh

    Setting keys:

      To set master key:
      % setenv HORUS_KEY_TYPE master
      % setenv HORUS_KEY_VALUE master-secret

      To set range key: (not tested)
      % setenv HORUS_KEY_TYPE 4,4
      % setenv HORUS_KEY_VALUE K4,4-secret

      To take effect for a file:
      % setenv HORUS_MATCH_FILE <filename> (case insensitive) (to be regex)



